Subject: Appliance is running low on disk space.
Description: Your appliance is running low on disk space, there is 3.54 gb free available from 40.69 gb (9%). EPP Server functionality and performance may be severely affected. Use Audit Log Backup to reduce the logs stored in the database, delete older system and audit log backups, and tune policies to reduce incoming log count. For further assistance contact Support.
Solution_Comment__c: The issue most likely is that the smtp you currently have configured on the EPP server(in order to generate alerts and send them via email to your smtp) is incorrect or something changed. This caused the mailer/alerts to occupy a lot of space on the disk. You mentioned you will ask a colleague to take a look over the smtp.
